queries.query: INSERT INTO `api_accesslogs` (`vIPAddress`, `vAPIName`, `vAPIURL`, `dAccessDate`, `vPlatform`, `vBrowser`, `vFileName`) VALUES ('103.118.146.38', 'notification', 'http://18.211.58.235/canoodle/WS/notification', '2020-11-04 12:28:50', 'Unknown OS Platform', 'Unknown Browser', 'notification-1604492930.json')

SELECT `n`.`iNotificationId` AS `notification_id`,`n`.`dtAddedAt` AS `notification_date`,`n`.`eNotificationType` AS `notification_type`,`n`.`vNotificationMessage` AS `message`,`u`.`iUserId` AS `notification_user_id`,concat(u.vFirstName,' ',u.vLastName) AS user_name,('') AS connection_type_by_logged_user,('') AS connection_type_by_receiver_user,`u`.`vProfileImage` AS `user_image` FROM `notification` AS `n` LEFT JOIN `users` AS `u` ON `n`.`iUserId` = `u`.`iUserId` WHERE `n`.`iNotifierId` = '13' AND `u`.`eStatus` = 'Active' ORDER BY `n`.`dtAddedAt` DESC

SELECT '' AS connection_type,                          (SELECT eConnectionType                          FROM user_connections                          WHERE eStatus='active' AND iUserId=13 AND  iConnectionUserId = 16) AS connection_type_by_logged_user,                         (SELECT eConnectionResult                          FROM user_connections                          WHERE eStatus='active' AND iUserId=13 AND  iConnectionUserId = 16) AS connection_result_by_logged_user,                         (SELECT eConnectionType                          FROM user_connections                          WHERE eStatus='active' AND iUserId=16 AND  iConnectionUserId = 13) AS connection_type_by_receiver_user,                         (SELECT eConnectionResult                          FROM user_connections                          WHERE eStatus='active' AND iUserId=16 AND  iConnectionUserId = 13) AS connection_result_by_receiver_user                                                  FROM user_connections LIMIT 1
